{"tid":2515974,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"澳門特區政府設立「融入國家發展工作委員會」","createTime":"2021-05-04T10:39:31.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-05T11:13:20.000Z","uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2b4f248391b8033b22313362e7ee51c67009df43","tid":2515974,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T10:39:31.000Z","msg":"澳門特區政府設立「融入國家發展工作委員會」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1589148-20210504.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1589148-20210504.htm&d=4vQCcaBbFH%2F4J6PBkjxGnkzKa5je2Ql9GrxhcbxOrro%3D&h=2dbecfbb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1589148-20210504.htm&h=021fd322\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1589148-20210504.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n澳門新聞局公布，為統籌澳門特區政府參與國家「一帶一路」建設及粵港澳大灣區建設，《澳門特別行政區公報》當天刊登行政長官批示，設立「融入國家發展工作委員會」，明日生效。<br />\n<br />\n根據批示，委員會的職能包括統籌澳門特區參與助力國家「一帶一路」建設及參與粵港澳大灣區建設的短、中、長期的總體設計及工作部署，並制定相關政策。<br />\n<br />\n委員會隸屬澳門行政長官運作，並由行政長官擔任主席。委員會下設若干工作組，政策研究和區域發展局向委員會提供運作所需的行政、技術及後勤支援。"},{"pid":"68107332cf4dbbffd33c6adfc301f3615b91ae70","tid":2515974,"uid":143241,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T10:40:43.000Z","msg":"我以為1966年就已經融合咗"},{"pid":"302e0c91024fc05eea08210fab47f1a956dfe1cf","tid":2515974,"uid":389615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"68107332cf4dbbffd33c6adfc301f3615b91ae70","tid":2515974,"uid":143241,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T10:40:43.000Z","msg":"我以為1966年就已經融合咗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T10:42:32.000Z","msg":"無人討論呢單新聞？"},{"pid":"bf3c9f65e498ae2b32d7984d429a5f2ab716f1ca","tid":2515974,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T11:13:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}